lead_paragraph: Boca Juniors midfielder Fernando Gago will be hoping for a lucky break when he faces River Plate on Sunday, having ruptured his Achilles tendon in both his previous two appearances in Argentina's "superclasico".

headline.print_headline: Boca's Gago Out to End River Plate Achilles Jinx
headline.main: Boca's Gago Out to End River Plate Achilles Jinx
